main event: Three small unidentified objects were observed in Keller, Washington, performing or conforming to a flight plan at high speed for approximately 25 seconds.
interesting points: The sighting took place during a clear night with no sound reported during the observation., The objects were assumed to be part of three succeeding flights., The visual details were sketched on the report to indicate the object's position relative to the observer., This incident was documented as part of the Project Blue Book investigations., The conclusion suggested the possibility of them being aircraft or missile verification flights.
